\tabular{rcc}{ \tab Reference \tab \cr Predicted \tab Positive \tab Negative
\cr Positive \tab A \tab B \cr Negative \tab C \tab D \cr }

The formulas used here are:

\deqn{Sensitivity = A/(A+C)}
